docs.title: Welcome to My Notes
docs.text: Here, you'll find a comprehensive collection of resources covering key concepts, programming languages, libraries, tools, and frameworks. Additionally, this repository includes documentation for various mini projects, curated code snippets, and a list of custom libraries developed to simplify the use of integrated libraries.
